249
00:12:47,580 --> 00:12:50,250
Sengoku Kakeru-kun.

250
00:12:50,250 --> 00:12:51,450
Vâng.

251
00:13:08,450 --> 00:13:09,330
Diễn...

252
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:15,750
Mình lỡ hắt hơi rồi.

253
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:24,790
Diễn văn...

254
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:28,580
